lead_paragraph: Brazil's six-game winning streak has rejuvenated the five times world champions and put them on the verge of reaching the 2018 finals in Russia with new coach Tite aiming to build on form that even he has found surprising.

headline.print_headline: Resurgent Brazil Almost Ready for Russia, Says Coach
